Package game.environments.spawn

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    EnemyFactory
    An interface for spawning enemies in the game
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Barrack
    Class that represents the spawning environment for godrick soldiers
    Cage
    Class that represents the spawning environment for dogs
    Dragonbarrow
    Class that represents the spawning environment for lesser dragons
    EastFactory
    A class for spawning enemies on the east side of the map
    Graveyard
    Class that represents the Graveyard SpawningGround which can spawn the HeavySkeletalSwordsman and SkeletalBandit
    GustOfWind
    Class that represents the GustofWind SpawningGround which can spawn the LoneWolf and GiantDog
    PuddleOfWater
    A class which represents the PuddleOfWater SpawningGround that spawns GiantCrabs and GiantCrayfish
    SpawningGround
    A class that represents the abstract class SpawningGround, representing all ground that will spawn an actor.
    WestFactory
    A class for spawning enemies on the west side of the map
